flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Start([Initialize Repository])
    Start([Initialize Repository]) --> Main[main branch (production)]
    Main[main branch (production)] --> Develop[develop branch]
    Develop[develop branch] --> Feature[feature/* branches]
    Feature[feature/* branches] --> Release[release/* branch]
    Release[release/* branch] --> Hotfix[hotfix/* branch]
    Hotfix[hotfix/* branch] --> MergeDev[Merge to develop]
    MergeDev[Merge to develop] --> MergeMain[Merge to main]
    MergeMain[Merge to main] --> Tag[Tag release]
    Tag[Tag release] --> Deploy[Deploy]